<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَسِرُّ المَسْأَلَةِ:</span> أَنَّهُ إِذَا قَالَ: أَنَا لَا أُشْرِكُ بِاللَّهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَقُلْ لَهُ:</span> وَمَا الشِّرْكُ بِاللَّهِ؟ فَسِّرْهُ لِي!<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَإِنْ قَالَ:</span> هُوَ عِبَادَةُ الأَصْنَامِ!<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَقُلْ:</span> وَمَا مَعْنَى عِبَادَةِ الأَصْنَامِ؟ فَسِّرْهَا لِي!<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَإِنْ قَالَ:</span> أَنَا لَا أَعْبُدُ إِلَّا اللَّهَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَقُلْ:</span> مَا مَعْنَى عِبَادَةِ اللَّهِ وَحْدَهُ؟ فَسِّرْهَا لِي!<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَإِنْ فَسَّرَهَا بِمَا بَيَّنَهُ القُرْآنُ؛ فَهُوَ المَطْلُوبُ، وَإِنْ لَمْ يَعْرِفْهُ؛ فَكَيْفَ يَدَّعِي شَيْئاً وَهُوَ لَا يَعْرِفُهُ؟<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>